entre (FMC) in Gusau for treatment. He then warns motorists against dangerous driving including wrongful overtaking and over-speeding as “those are the major causes of road crashes”. (NAN) Vanguard News Nigeria. Three passengers, a female and two males, lost their lives while 10 others sustained various degrees of injury in a multiple accident on Ijebu-Ode-Ore expressway yesterday. March 28, 2018 In "News" Namoda (Zamfara)—At least 20 persons have been confirmed dead, while 33 others sustained serious injuries in two motor accidents in Zamfara, Sunday. November 1, 2010 In "News" The Federal Road Safety Commission (FRSC) in Zamfara has confirmed the death of 14 people in a motor accident at Wanzamai Village on Gusau-Zaria road in Tsafe Local Government Area of the state. November 13, 2011 In "News"